HEADWORD: Sententiary
<hw>Sen*ten"ti*ary</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>sententiarius</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who read lectures, or
commented, on the Sentences of Peter Lombard, Bishop of Paris
(1159-1160), a school divine.</def> <rj><au>R. Henry.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

